<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8">{{> base-styles}}</head>
<body>
  <div class="sheet">
    {{> letterhead}}

    <div class="doc-head">
      <div class="doc-eyebrow">Private &amp; Confidential</div>
      <h1 class="doc-title">Letter of Promotion</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="meta-row">
      <div>
        <span class="meta-k">Reference No.</span>
        <span class="meta-v">{{refNo}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="right">
        <span class="meta-k">Date of Issue</span>
        <span class="meta-v">{{generatedDate}}</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="salutation">Dear {{fullName}},</p>
      <p>
        We are delighted to inform you that, in recognition of your consistent
        performance and valuable contributions to <strong>{{companyName}}</strong>, you
        have been promoted to the position of <strong>{{newJobTitle}}</strong>{{#if newDepartment}}
        in the <strong>{{newDepartment}}</strong> department{{/if}}, effective
        <strong>{{effectiveDate}}</strong>.
      </p>

      <table class="kv">
        <tr><th>Current Designation</th><td>{{jobTitle}}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>New Designation</th><td>{{newJobTitle}}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Department</th><td>{{#if newDepartment}}{{newDepartment}}{{else}}{{department}}{{/if}}</td></tr>
        <tr><th>Effective Date</th><td>{{effectiveDate}}</td></tr>
        {{#if newSalaryFormatted}}<tr><th>Revised Annual CTC</th><td>{{newSalaryFormatted}} per annum</td></tr>{{/if}}
      </table>

      <p>
        Your new role carries greater responsibility, and we are confident that you will
        continue to excel and inspire those around you. All other terms and conditions of
        your employment remain unchanged unless communicated separately.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please accept our heartfelt congratulations on this well-deserved advancement. We
        look forward to your continued success.
      </p>

      <div class="sign">
        <p style="margin:0 0 6px; font-size:10px; color:var(--muted);">With best wishes,</p>
        <div class="sign__space"></div>
        <div class="sign__rule"></div>
        <div class="sign__name">{{signatoryName}}</div>
        <div class="sign__title">{{signatoryTitle}}</div>
        <div class="sign__title">{{companyName}}</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{> footer}}
  </div>
</body>
</html>
